| # | Task | Status | Notes |
|---|------|--------|-------|
| 12.1 | **Backend Leads Endpoint** | ✅ DONE | Added `GET /events/{event_id}/leads` endpoint in `main.py` (guarded by event ownership). |
| 12.2 | **Dashboard Export** | ✅ DONE | Added CSV export button in `Dashboard.tsx` and `Admin.tsx` event cards → calls leads endpoint → downloads as CSV. |
